      "statement": "If M_pad\u22641 then N_ord=N_side (v20) and A_SP payment reduces to injecting ordered free-1 CS e-set pairs into a set of size \u2264 t\u00b7p. Deployed t=e=w+1, so the natural budget is e\u00b7p = t\u00b7p = 143763024447376.",
      "status": "PROVED"
    }
  },
